# 5. Plane of symmetry pressure measurements
1. There are two types of distribution. 
	1. For $UD/v < 5000$, the curves have minima
	2. while for $UD/v > 5000$ no minima can be seen.
	
2. As $UD/\nu$ and $D/\delta^{*}$ increase $C_{p}$ at $x/D = -0.5$ also increases.
		![[Figure 10..png]]

3. it can be seen that the vortex moves away from the model as $D/\delta^{*}$decreases.
